high_descs: Turn around and pick the cleaning brush from the toilet.
Again turn around and go straight
Go straight and head towards the sink.
Put the soapbar into the sink and pour the water.
Take back the brush and go back to the toilet where picked the brush.
Keep the soapbar on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Pick the SoapBar clean it and keep it on the same Toilet

high_descs: Pick up the white soapbar from the top of the toilet.
Walk up to the sink on the left.
Wash the soapbar in the sink and take it out.
Walk back to the toilet on the right.
Put the soapbar on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put the SoapBar on the Toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the toilet
Pick up soap bar from the toilet
Turn around towards the sink at the back
Place soap bar inside the sink and then take it out
Turn right and turn left and then head straight towards the toilet
Place soap bar on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Washing soap bar on the sink and placing it on toilet
